==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Prier
<hw>Pri"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Pry</er>.]</ety> <def>One who pries; one who inquires narrowly and
searches, or is inquisitive.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>So pragmatical a <qex>prier</qex> he is into divine secrets.</q>
<rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Priest</ent>⟦br⟧
